HEADWORD: Cerebrum
<hw>Cer"e*brum</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it> E.
<plw>Cerebrums</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>, L. <plw>Cerebra</plw>
